task_score.transcript: You are a senior college student. Liu Hong is a new student in your apartment. You are aware that your home has been under a lot of stress with study and his own treatment for depression. This morning, Lu Hong asks you to have a ride at one of her final essays and offer her some feedback. You read the the essay and notice it was badly written with chunks of. Paraphrase. Uh, plagiarized from other sources, Lu Hong tells you she had to submit this paper. Tomorrow morning, you decide to send her voice message to talk about her essay.
